data.title: BRONX BOARD
data.meta_description: The BRONX BOARD is a WorldWideWeb-based bulletin board for ex-Bronxites to find old school friends, talk about the Bronx, and revive old connections lost over the years since they walked the streets of  their beloved borough.
data.text:
